libwtclasses (1.0.5-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * new upstream (build system, not source)
  * add ${python:Depends} to wtclasses-progs
        fix python-script-but-no-python-dep error
  * do not set useless x bit while installing
        fix executable-not-elf-or-script warning
  * do not link against -lboost_system
        fix dpkg-shlibdeps warning
  * add soname to .so file, follow Debian Policy, 8.1 Run-time shared libraries
        fix sharedobject-in-library-directory-missing-soname error
  * add ${shlibs:Depends} to examples
        fix missing-dependency-on-libc error
  * add ${misc:Depends} to all packages
        fix debhelper-but-no-misc-depends warning

 -- Boris Nagaev <bnagaev@gmail.com>  Sat, 26 Nov 2011 23:43:41 +0400

